Ace Should Surpass Market Growth, CEO Greenberg Tells Finanz

-- B y   C a r o l y n   B a n d e l
-- 
2011-05-21T10:11:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-21/ace-should-surpass-market-growth-ceo-greenberg-tells-finanz.html
Ace Ltd. (ACE)  should be able to “exceed
the market growth” in property and casualty insurance, Chief
Executive Officer Evan Greenberg was cited as saying in an
interview with  Finanz und Wirtschaft .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carolyn Bandel in Zurich at 
 cbandel@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at   fconnelly@bloomberg.net . 